title: HPSC Assistant Engineer Civil Group B Online Form 2026 for 50 Post
description: HPSC Assistant Engineer Recruitment 2026: Apply for Civil Group B 50 Post Post Update Date: 09-01-2026 Short Description: HPSC Assistant Engineer Group B Online Form 2026: Haryana Public Service Commission has announced recruitment for 50 Posts of Haryana PSC Assistant Engineer Group B. Candidates who want to apply online can apply from the link given on Rojgar Result. Haryana Assistant Engineer Online Form 2026 can be filled from 13 January 2026 to 12 Febuary2026.
